Barbara Whiting Smith https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Whiting_Smith 0 Barbara Whiting Smith (May 19, 1931 – June 9, 2004) was an actress in movies and on radio and television, primarily in the 1940s and 1950s.
